</A>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
ccs-init - Load TOMOYO Linux&#146;s policy automatically
<!-- .SH SYNOPSIS -->
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<A name=contents></A><H3>CONTENTS</H3></A>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
